name: Satella Walker 2: Dai-1-wa: Mokumoku Kemuri Panic
overview: SatellaWalker 2 is a Downloadable 2-part Soundlink game for the Satellaview that was broadcast between February 15, 1998 and February 28, 1998. SatellaWalker 2 was broadcast as the sequel to the earlier-broadcast SatellaWalker of July 1997.
